data.title: RESISTANCE Party, DJ Listings, Tours & Tickets
data.meta_description: In accordance with the Balearic Government's restrictions on nightclubs in Ibiza, the Resistance summer residency at Privilege will not take place this summer.
data.text:
Resistance Ibiza is a name that shines bright, as it delivers parties across the globe in every continent. Resistance is especially known for integrating the best of the best in the worldwide underground techno industry and for hosting some of the most eye-catching music festivals. This underground ultra label has become one of the hottest parties on the island ever since its inception in 2017.

The party is home to the best quality of techno music and to add to the marvel, light shows and lasers, combined with the brilliant structures of the venue intensify the environment, turning this electrifying experience into a memorable one.

Resistance has been known to host various mega names in the electronic music industry such as Richie Hawtin, Maceo Plex, Jamie Jones, Loco Dice, Pan-Pot, Sasha and John Digweed, Nicole Moudaber, Testpilot, Joris Voorn and Nic Fanciulli. The line-up of 2019 included Eats Everything, Sasha, Carl Cox, Charlotte de Witte, Adam Beyer and Paco Osuna.
